libcalvin-perl (1.04-1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
    - Install man pages for things with POD documentation.
    - Fix bots to ignore undef given to setters, fixing an issue where
      config loading was wiping out defaults.
    - Fix syntax errors in URL_Store.pm (not currently used).
    - Remove unnecessary use of Crypt.
  * Add all runtime dependencies to Build-Depends so that syntax tests
    will succeed during the build.
  * Add Depends on libhtml-entities-perl and libjson-perl.
  * Update standards version to 4.1.4 (no changes required).

 -- Russ Allbery <rra@debian.org>  Sun, 22 Apr 2018 10:09:18 -0700

libcalvin-perl (1.03-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Jon Robertson ]
  * Add libdate-manip-perl to dependencies.
  * New upstream release.
    - Add manual pages for logread and loggrep.
    - New logfind script to search logs by tags.
    - Save logread errors file to the running user's home directory.
    - Fix Cambot errors when a user bot doesn't have all the same things
      set as the system bot, such as autojoins.

  [ Russ Allbery ]
  * Add upstream-vcs-tag pattern to debian/gbp.conf.

 -- Russ Allbery <rra@debian.org>  Sat, 17 Mar 2018 21:39:28 -0700

libcalvin-perl (1.02-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Remove libdata-dumper-perl dependency, since this module is part of
    Perl core and has no separate existence.

 -- Russ Allbery <rra@debian.org>  Sat, 03 Feb 2018 11:18:55 -0800

libcalvin-perl (1.02-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
    - Switch uberbot to YAML conifg files and rewrite config file handling
      to no longer use internal strings that are created and reparsed.
    - New uberbot-config-upgrade script to update uberbot config files.
    - Redo uberbot STDERR handling to only redirect to a file if a
      filename is given as an argument.
    - Clean up command names in plexchar-* documentation and help.
    - Run help if no arguments are given to plexchar-search.
    - Fix use of a testing directory for $ROOTDIR in Calvin::Tag.
    - Add new Calvin::Bots::Charcters bot that provides read-only
      plexchar-search functionality.

 -- Russ Allbery <rra@debian.org>  Sat, 03 Feb 2018 11:15:53 -0800

