libcalvin-perl (1.01-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Jon Robertson ]
  * Add missing libconfig-simple-perl, libhash-merge-perl, libcurses-perl,
    libcurses-ui-perl, libgetopt-long-descriptive-perl, libnet-remctl-perl,
    libperl6-slurp-perl dependencies.

  [ Russ Allbery ]
  * New upstream release.
    - Unify Cambot session-list commands into one command with options
      parsed with Getopt::Long.
    - Add new Cambot session-list commands for searching pending sessions.
    - Adjust uberbot error log file location.
  * Add missing libdate-calc-perl and libfile-homedir-perl dependencies.

